            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audia</ex></expan> Ursa vix<lb break="no" n="2"/>it annos II dies X Ges<lb break="no" n="3"/>atia Lucia vixit an<lb break="no" n="4"/>nos IIII &amp;lt;f=E&amp;gt;ecit <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> Do<lb break="no" n="5"/>natus <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> III <expan><abbr>Ital</abbr><ex>icae</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>et Pedania Profutur<lb break="no" n="7"/>a parentes vivi filia<lb break="no" n="8"/>bus suis memoria <lb n="9"/>fecerunt 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Im Giebel Nische mit Büsten eines Ehepaares mit zwei Kindern. Text 1 befindet sich in der Nische zwischen den Büsten. Datierung nach Mander wg. Frisurtypus severisch. (B): CIL 03, 05947; Mander: Z. 5: fecit.</p>
